# CODEOWNERS — KETIV-Technologies-Inc/.github
#
# Routes review requests automatically when a PR touches matching paths.
# Owners listed here are auto-requested as reviewers; if branch protection
# requires CODEOWNERS approval, the PR is blocked until one of them approves.
#
# Pattern syntax matches .gitignore. First match in this file wins per path —
# so more-specific rules go *below* more-general ones.
#
# Reference:
#   https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# NOTE: Team slug `github-admins` is assumed. Verify the exact slug at
#   https://github.com/orgs/Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/teams
# A wrong slug fails silently — GitHub will not request the review and will
# not flag the CODEOWNERS file as invalid in the PR UI.

# ---- Default catch-all ----
# Everything in this repo, unless overridden below.
*                              @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins

# ---- Public marketing surface ----
# profile/README.md renders at github.com/Ketiv-Technologies-Inc and should
# pass the same review bar as the company homepage.
/profile/                      @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins

# ---- Org-wide GitHub defaults ----
# These propagate to every repo in the org that doesn't override them.
# Changes affect all maintainers org-wide, so they belong here for review.
/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/               @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins
/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE.md      @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins
/workflow-templates/           @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins

# ---- Org automation manifest ----
# This tree is the source of truth for what the Ketiv.GitHub.Automation
# function applies to every repo in the org. Merging fires sync-manifest.yml
# which writes the spec to App Configuration. PRs here must be reviewed.
/org-automation/               @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins

# ---- Sync workflow ----
# Touching the manifest sync workflow can break org-wide automation rollouts.
/.github/workflows/sync-manifest.yml @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins

# ---- Repo governance ----
# Changes to these files affect how the repo itself is governed.
/CODEOWNERS                    @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins
/.gitattributes                @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins
/.gitignore                    @Ketiv-Technologies-Inc/github-admins
